Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,MAAM'S DECISION
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold still. Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever made this is a genius.\NIt's completely beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody come check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Marin of the Troika...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Behoma?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The greatest Hoimi! Spell\Nthat the Princess can cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It can cure severe injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There. You're all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. A friend in need and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad, Marin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona's so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously.\NShe's a Sage in training after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She can even use attack spells,\Nthough not as strong as the Troika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's truly an all-around spell caster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to talk with Uncle Matorif.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he can fix my Magic Bullet Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like your Magic Power's increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let that surprise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Gira!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyado!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Iora!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:04:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Flight Spell, Toberura.\NWhen did you learn that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy if you know Rura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Toberura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be old, but in a one-minute\None-on-one fight
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there isn't a being alive\Nwho can beat me at magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nasty old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Matorif, can't you teach me\Nsome amazing spells, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having you do basic meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're teaching Popp\Nand he's improving so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool. You don't need to know\Nthe same spells as Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hero can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But a Warrior is stronger,\Nand a Mage can do more magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hero is a jack-of-all-trades\Nand master of none.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But a Hero does possess an ultimate weapon\Nthat no one else has.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hero's weapon is courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All you need is the courage\Nto face any enemy. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want magic,\Nthis one will improve on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes a party.\NThat's what companions are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Courage, huh?\NI suppose that's something I don't have.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A weapon of my own.\NThat's it. Without that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mere presence oozes salaciousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just hide my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:06:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, the one thing you take after\Nyour father, Roka, is your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Strength? My father's strength...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Papunica Kingdom is gradually rebuilding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hearing Dai beat the Dark Army,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the citizens are returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The temple repairs will soon be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we can start on the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Things seem to be going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Which leaves us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army's fortress is here\Nin the mountains of Guildmain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Maam, Crocodine and Hyunckel\Nwent on a reconnaissance mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, we lack weapons and manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than attack,\Nwe should focus on building our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Then let's all\Ngo look for new weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds good. Right, Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, everyone. I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I should go\Nmy own way for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! How come?! Why so suddenly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With my Magic Bullet Gun broken,\NI can't use spells to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus Leona is far better at Hoimi Spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'm going to end up\Nbeing a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll likely be facing\Nfar more powerful enemies from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Without greater power,\Nyou really may end up being a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, that's a little harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You never hold back, Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:08:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought\NI should return to Romos to train.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To find something only I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's something only you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Martial arts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I figured I'd become\Na Martial Artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A Martial Artist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel and Crocodine have betrayed us,\Nand Flazzard is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Six Legion Commanders\Nnow three, our forces are halved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This melody is the Reaper Flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I told you!\NHadorra's army is falling apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:09:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy, Piroro.\NYou were wise to inform me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings, inhabitants of Sovereign\NRock Castle. Let me introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,KILBAN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kilban.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Piroro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is Kilban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you've heard of him!\NThe personal assassin of Dark King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The deadly reaper of the Dark Army\Nthat silently erases
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,those who cross King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And why is the reaper here\Nin Sovereign Rock Castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Has someone's incompetence\Nwarranted a visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is surprising, Mist.\NI haven't heard you speak in decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprise, surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen you remain silent for centuries\Nwhen there's nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who talks to much, Kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do these two know each other?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, Hadorra, I hear your performance\Nhas been slipping as of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NHe's been botching things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since he failed to kill Dai the Hero,\NLegion Commanders have fallen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Romos and Papunica were reclaimed.\NIt's a whole mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And recently, he took the whole army\Nand was still beaten by Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true you let\NDai and his friends beat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan to kill him\Nis still ongoing! In time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'd better hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban is a patient man,\Nbut even he has his limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you should fail again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fail, then what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have to say it? This. Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:11:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then have no fear!\NI'll wipe out those brats in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,By my own hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The next to fight Dai is me,\NDragon Master General Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:15.57,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEHOMA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NHEAL-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,MAGIC BULLET GUN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's too soon!\NHas he already destroyed Carl Kingdom?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our savior Baran! How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. You've been saving\NDragon Master General Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess there's no issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Baran! In order to regain\Nthe Dark King's trust, I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Commander,\NI grow tired of your excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know why you seek\Nto keep me away from Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy, Dai,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is a Dragon Knight, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A Dragon Knight?! From the legends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He finally knows!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, will you leave Dai to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No, No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As Dark Commander, I order you!\NYou will do nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there is no proof\Nthat he's really a Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely need to see it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I know what's going on, Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If this Dai really is a Dragon Knight,\Nyou can't let Baran near him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, you can all squabble\Non your own time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to finish what I came here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the Key of Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine and Hyunckel, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two know the location\Nof Sovereign Rock Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So King Ban ordered me\Nto move it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It finally stands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sovereign Rock Castle moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, let's all enjoy\Na little globe-trotting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whee! Whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't she just train with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a decision she reached\Nafter much thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I've heard deep in the mountains\Nof Romos lives a "God of Martial Arts."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about some God of Martial Arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let her go off and\Nbe a Martial Artist or whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so sour about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp's actually sad\Nbecause he really likes Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really? Then why don't you\Njust tell her how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be seeing her\Nfor a while anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,For... a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.\NShe's already into someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you're all sour?\NIs that supposed to be kindness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, if you die in battle,\Nthis will be your final farewell to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll never know how you feel.\NAre you fine with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is... our final farewell?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And off he goes! What will happen now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, you're enjoying this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to Nayle Village\Nin Romos, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you there with Rura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What will he do?\NWill he be able to tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That was mean, Leona.\NTo push Popp like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.\NI said what I said for his benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good for one's mental health\Nto keep things bottled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not going to Nayle Village?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You said Romos, so I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Our battle isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not returning there until we defeat\Nthe Dark Army and avenge Master Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the God of Martial Arts is\Nsaid to live deep in the Romos mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I trained in the Romos mountains\Nwith Mentor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get there with Rura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on. We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I guess I'll take you up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Rura!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! He even put his arm around her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad job at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good luck, Maam. We'll be waiting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. My landings still suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This isn't the Romos mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the Dark Forest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did we end up here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,where we first met!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. A mental image\Nis the key to Rura spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this place\Nis really important to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember. The first thing we did\Nwhen we met was fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The timing feels right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my chance to tell her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it took us days by boat\Nfrom Romos to Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can come back in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When we first met, I couldn't imagine\Nyou doing something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, at first I thought\Nyou were just a selfish coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, through every battle,\Nyou grew so strong and so brave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It made me realize\Nhow hard you were trying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You grew strong so fast\Nand learned new spells,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and saved me again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even back when we fought Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, after that battle,\NI decided I wanted to catch up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have you rescuing me\Nall the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Maam. It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to feel that way at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd gladly throw my life away\Nfor you any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to tell you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"I..."?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're the best companion ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll be back.\NYou'll be shocked how strong I become.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you show up looking like\Nsome muscle-bound gorilla,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pretend I don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already not much to look at now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Best of luck out there!\NTry not to become a muscle-bound gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is how it should be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't tell her yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not at strong or brave\Nas she thinks I am!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to get even stronger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's a 70 to 80% chance\Nthat he gets shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are enjoying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sovereign Rock Castle is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sovereign Rock Castle has moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying the castle\Nsprouted legs and walked away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not entirely impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,considering Dark King Ban's\NSupercharged Dark Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, you need to inform\NDai and the others of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to follow\Nthose giant footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel something terrible\Nis going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost at the northernmost land\Nknown as the Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are smooth, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge! It's enormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A giant made of rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:32.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:36.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:52.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:01.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
